Landscape mode! Fixed recording sync issue Fixed recording issue with song loading after stopping restarting Fixed crash issue when singing in Practice Mode Fixed issue with displaying recording date times Optimized Listen Player flow Fixed My Recordings search UI issues Fixed issue with User Profile changes not being retained Added Producer Labels on backing tracks Fixed UI issue with updating User Status Fixed UI issues with views loves comment counts Fixed UI issue with user avatar on main menu Optimized Sign Up account verification Removed Trending Recordings sections Removed free label from backing tracks Improved SingSnap Store flow for purchasing credits Added ability for users to delete their accounts

Fixed that annoying issue with the mic cutting out in the recorder Added pagination to Playlists Fixed blocking redirect error Fixed unblock option when user has long status message Fixed appearance of User Status message Fixed issue with first frame of recorder being dark Fixed appearance of Harmony recordings in My Recordings and Listen Player Changed recording limit message for blue users Fixed Favorites drop down menu Adjustments for iOS 14 compatibility
Bug fixes We got rid of that annoying error that happened sometimes when you clicked on a profile or recording Also fixed the error that happened when entering the Recorder.

Need to update your email address or password You can do that in the app now! Want to record with a Bluetooth devices You can do that too! Now you can send gifts to members from the User Profile Listen Player! That crash you experienced while recording the perfect recording we know we re sorry! we fixed the bug! Adjusted the side mute button behavior so it will no longer mute audio from our app. Updated some behind the scene items making sure you have the latest recording technology We also added some items to improve our support staff s qualify of life. Adding some polish finishing touches to ensure iOS 14 compatibility.

Remember that annoying instance when the app seemed to be loading fine but all the sections were empty No Good! But we fixed it anyway. Pesky recordings sometimes made the whole thing crash we isolated the instances and squashed quite a few bugs let us know if we missed some! Added auto update functionality for new releases
